      "content": "i'm not really sure what you mean by \"goblin hunt\"? i just need technical debugging steps. can you stick to the actual tools? specifically, for an embedded system where i might not be able to run heavy profilers like Valgrind, what are some lighter weight ways to monitor heap usage or catch the specific allocation that's failing?",
